OL,5, Tributes have flooded in following the 
OL,6, death of veteran sports reporter Bob   
OL,7, Hall.                                  
OL,9,FOver a career spanning four decades, Mr
OL,10,FHall became a well-known and respected 
OL,11,Fsports journalist in the Midlands.     
OL,13,FHe was best known for his reporting at 
OL,14,FITV Central, Sky Sports Soccer Saturday
OL,15,Fand Black Country Radio.               
OL,17,FMidlands football clubs led tributes   
OL,18,Fonline to Mr Hall, who they described  
OL,19,Fas a "respected figure in the press    
OL,20,Fbench".                                
